Summary
This is a repo for writing testcase in playwright + TS tempraryly for a private web. 
The purpose for this is to understand the test frame and put it into use.

Installation
Node.js
VSCode
Playwright

Setup the Enviroment
# Creat a new folder
# Open it in VSCode
# Ctrl + Shift + X to find the Playwright Test for VSCode and click Install
# Ctrl + Shift + P to find the Test: Install Playwright, remember to check the JS if you gonna develop your test in JS, you can uncheck the webdriver if you don't want all the default ones
# Check on console to confirm all steps finished successfully
# You can start with your testcase writing now

Reference
https://playwright.dev/docs/writing-tests